## ğŸš€ Prerequisites

### ğŸ”§ Local Machine

- Node.js (v18+ recommended)
- npm
- Expo CLI (`npm install -g expo-cli`)
- MySQL (e.g. XAMPP or MySQL server running locally)

### ğŸ“± Mobile Environment

